name: Tabs
body:
### Welcome to Tabs for Reddit
Tabs for Reddit is a minimalistic Android client for Reddit.

#### Alpha/Beta Testing
Participate in the open alpha/beta testing by downloading the app in [HockeyApp](https://rink.hockeyapp.net/apps/2a2a77e1284e414abc97f02562d01af4)
